---
title: Golden Ginger-Scallion Sea Bass  with Steamed Rice and Umami-Glazed Veggies
description: Savoury, aromatic ginger-scallion oil is a beloved Cantonese condiment that can be used raw, but for this dish, we're opting to stir it into hot oil for a mild but sizzling treatment. Adding layers of flavour could not be any easier with this sauce technique, and your dinner table will be better for it.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R1044_W31_CA_RF26096-1_Main_low-afaea7cc.jpg
